Title: Work Order: Shado-Pan I
Description:
<Yoon's writing seems rushed. He must have been excited.>

The Shado-Pan want crops from you! What an honor indeed!

A request came in this morning for green cabbages. Apparently, they make a rather tasty cabbage soup with them.

Only the finest will do for the Shado-Pan!
ObjectivesText: Plant 8 Green Cabbage Seeds on Sunsong Ranch.
